Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:28.06,lassie episode,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:83688,88067}{\blur0.5\fad(300,0)\pos(320,290)}I Don't Like Lassie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93156,95241}Here it is! Come look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:36.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95241,96826}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96826,98786}If you need to set your clock,\Nnow's the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98786,100538}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100538,102582}It's five to three.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:43.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102582,103583}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:47.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103583,107253}This dog walks by at the same time\Nevery day, like clockwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108421,110840}The clock at our home\Nhas stopped working.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:54.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110840,114052}Now this is how I tell time.\NStrange, isn't itt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124228,125021}Hey, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:07.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125647,127190}You're walking him today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:08.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127190,128024}Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129942,131319}I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132362,134656}I'm afraid I can't\Nunderstand you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165895,168564}How come you\Ndon't know the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169065,170566}Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172276,174821}No, I really do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174821,176864}That is just deplorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:03:01.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176864,181369}I explained it in great detail just minutes ago.\NWhat were you doing during that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182078,183746}Don't stick out your tongue at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192797,195925}I can hear the bell, but we're not ending\Nuntil someone answers the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196259,197427}John Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197427,198344}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198344,200012}Answer the question I had asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201764,203099}Uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203099,205727}Three hundred… and forty…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:27.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205727,207019}No, twenty…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207019,208438}Excuse me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208688,209605}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209605,210773}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:33.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211399,213776}Can I sit already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:36.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215069,216195}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216195,217697}Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218281,220700}I can't believe it.\NHow did you even get an idea like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231252,233004}Geez, it's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233004,235298}I thought it was never gonna end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235298,236507}Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238092,240386}He was such a nag today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240386,242096}But Sandy's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242096,244974}He scolded her so bad\Nand she just laughed it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244974,248102}Even better, when he was\Nabout to explode, she was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248102,251522}"Can I sit already?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251522,254400}I wish I could be\Nhappy-go-lucky like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254400,255526}So what if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257945,260156}I'm just a happy-go-lucky\Ngirl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260156,261741}So sue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261741,264285}What's gotten into you, Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:28.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264285,268456}I'm just saying that I'm jealous\Nthat you're always so cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:32.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268456,272460}Because I didn't know the answer,\Nhe moved on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:37.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272460,277006}I tried to give you\Nmore time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277298,278883}But that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:43.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278883,283679}Yes, I know, I made him even\Nmadder by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:47.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283679,287433}See? I'm not as happy-go-lucky\Nas you say I am, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297485,298194}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298194,299612}Hey, Lassie.\NBye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299612,301656}No use waiting for him.\NYou can thank Sandy for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:03.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301656,303991}Don't say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:19.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316379,319382}Did you wait for John\Nall this time, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319382,320424}How admirable of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321509,324136}See you, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:36.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332937,336649}I think it's better\Nif you apologize, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336649,337441}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:40.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337441,340987}I have a lot of work at the store,\Nso I can't go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341696,344115}But think about it.\NSandy has to help her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344115,345616}That's why she\Nstruggles in classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346492,347869}So…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347869,349287}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349287,351122}All right, then. I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:56.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351122,356252}but I have to take the goods\Nfrom our store to the Mortons today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356252,357753}Hey, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359714,362633}Now even Colin left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378983,381777}I can't play with you today, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381777,383571}I just don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387742,388534}Eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:35.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391287,395166}But I have to admit, I didn't think\NSandy would get so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396000,397710}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:43.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398711,403257}Well, it is Sandy we're talking about.\NShe'll forget it by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403257,404926}Oh? Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:45.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404926,405801}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405801,408304}Doesn't Lassie need food today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408304,409722}Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409722,411432}What's the matter, lad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:55.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411432,415603}You mustn't forget to feed Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415603,417897}Thank you, Mr. Nelson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:01.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417897,421233}Also, we'll get more stock\Nfor this weekend as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421233,423527}Thanks. I'll tell Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423527,425196}Oh, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425196,427782}Weren't you guys\Na little late today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427782,430368}Did you get punished\Nbecause you haven't studied well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430368,431619}Ah, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431619,433829}She's such a good dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:14.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433829,434622}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435039,437249}We were just talking about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437249,440294}We've never seen a dog\Nwith such beautiful hair like hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440294,442296}Oh? I wonder about that…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442296,444590}I have to brush her every morning—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444590,446509}It's just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:30.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446509,450680}I wonder if the cold strong winds\Nin Yorkshire made her hair like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:31.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450680,451847}It's not like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:37.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451847,457395}That's right. As I said, Yorkshire dogs\Ngrow well even if the owner kicks them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:38.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457395,458896}Can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469407,471701}"Grow well even if the owner\Nkicks them out".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471701,473536}As if they knew anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479000,480876}Hey! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:05.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481168,485548}What are you doing?\NI can't believe you're digging again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486048,488259}Don't even think that\Nyou can go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488259,490886}You'll stain the whole house\Nlooking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491554,492888}Oh, for heaven's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494724,495891}Stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496517,498978}You do this every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498978,500104}Paw, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501731,503899}Look at you, all mucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504316,506402}I told you to stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507028,508696}Sounds rather serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508696,510031}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510031,513075}He understands the adult world\Na little bit better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:36.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513075,516203}John! I don't know\Nwhat happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516203,518164}but don't take it out on Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518164,520833}I'm not taking anything out on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520833,523836}Lassie can't do anything without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524045,525046}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525046,526088}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:50.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526464,530259}I always tell her to stay home\Nand wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530259,532636}Yet she follows me to school\Nevery morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532636,535723}and when I'm about to go back,\Nshe's already waiting in front of the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:56.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535723,536307}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536307,537516}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:01.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538100,541145}This water is not for drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541479,544273}All right, Lassie.\NWe're going upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566754,568047}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568047,570132}Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570132,571842}You're not a puppy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571842,573719}Sleep in your own place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575554,576680}Look at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576680,579725}I wonder what Mr. Nelson\Nwould say now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580267,582394}What an unruley bedhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582394,584647}Very beautiful hair, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594365,597118}You have fleas, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597118,599286}No wonder I've been all itchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599286,601497}Where did you get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:07.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606210,607461}Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614135,616011}I said, don't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616011,617888}I'm going to school by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617888,620141}Learn to play by yourself sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624019,625479}Sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625479,627815}You must have been\Nlooking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627815,630651}That's all right.\NI can't blame him for having a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:36.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631652,636073}Please tell Colin that I'd like to go\Nto school together when he's well again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636073,637700}No problem. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637700,639618}He should be fine tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639618,641245}– Good bye, sir.\N– Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:55.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652423,655050}I told you to stop\Nfollowing me everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655050,657136}Try walking somewhere\Non your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657636,658637}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:19.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676322,679533}Oh? She's gone already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679533,680659}What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702806,705935}Oh, Lassie.\NYou're here today again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706310,708938}Our Bingo is a bit old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:52.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708938,712942}I really appreciate\Nyour help with the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:55.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714109,715945}Good girl.
Comment: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:02.49,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:722493,722493}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:24.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741220,744723}I knew Colin would be absent,\Nbut Sandy, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745766,748644}I can't apologize\Nfor yesterday now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795607,798777}Oh? Looks like I forgot about one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799069,801864}You're such a smart dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801864,805909}You learned so much\Njust by staying around Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805909,808120}You're a fine sheepdog now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808120,809288}Right, Bingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810581,811749}All right, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811749,814043}I can take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814043,815336}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815336,817254}Here, this is for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817254,818255}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911306,912891}Well, it's her share for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913809,914852}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914852,916061}But, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:19.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916061,919314}It's not Yorkshire winds that\Nmade Lassie's hair like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919314,920649}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920649,923861}I'm brushing her hair every day\Nand that is why it looks so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923861,926405}Lassie can't do anything\Nwithout me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926780,928282}I… I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928282,930409}You're a good lad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931326,932369}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932369,934997}I'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934997,936290}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941086,943755}Did we say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943755,945799}Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980459,981919}Don't cling to me like a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996308,997601}Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999478,1001855}What are we going to play today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:48.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003857,1008237}Oh, right. There's an abandoned mine shaft.\NWhy don't we look for a treasure together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:11.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026838,1031093}It's been abandoned\Nfor many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032177,1034721}It's so dark and spooky inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035681,1037933}I wonder how far can you\Nfollow me, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037933,1040727}Even you won't be able to\Nfollow me for too much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041478,1042771}Alright, I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056535,1057411}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057411,1059454}This way, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091278,1093071}I used to play here\Na lot when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093071,1094698}I won't let her catch up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:23.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102748,1103624}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:32.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108337,1112758}How long is she going to chase me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122392,1123644}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123644,1125812}Hey! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129274,1131526}W-Wait there,\NI'll help you in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131526,1132486}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144915,1146333}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147334,1149419}I think this is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150379,1151338}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:17.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152923,1157844}Somehow the sky feels\Nmuch farther away than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:22.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160097,1162140}Is anybody going to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162849,1164267}Tell me, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165352,1167312}Lassie! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167312,1168730}Hey! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171149,1172776}Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172776,1175612}I thought you got hurt\Nor even died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:40.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177489,1180325}I'm really sorry, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:42.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180325,1182744}I don't know why, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:46.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182744,1186373}Seeing how everyone praised you\Nmade me kind of upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187082,1189292}I mean, I was very happy on one hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189292,1191128}but at the same time\NI felt kind of hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:54.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191878,1194131}I'm pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:20:00.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195465,1200595}I didn't think how Sandy would feel\Nand blurted out something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:04.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200595,1204683}I got depressed and took it on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:07.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204683,1207894}Even though you're my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210063,1211773}I'm sorry, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:15.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213400,1215277}I want to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216403,1219906}Bark something, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223744,1225370}Lassie… you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249311,1251104}What's up, Bingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254357,1256234}What? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261281,1262574}Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:03.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262949,1263909}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264534,1267245}What happened?\NJohn, did you fall here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267245,1269873}Wait a moment, I'll help you\Nget out in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:16.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275587,1276755}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277172,1278548}It's food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278548,1281009}Or more like, an apology\Nfor the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:24.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281009,1284387}You've been absent\Nfor the third day in a row, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284387,1286848}An apology? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286848,1288767}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289017,1290227}By the way, John,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290227,1292479}I took time off because\Nof a stomach ache.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:35.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292479,1295649}Why did you bring food?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:37.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295649,1297442}Your stomach hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:39.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297442,1299778}I thought you had a fever like Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301071,1303406}No problem.\NI'll eat it once I get well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:48.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304699,1308787}John, I'm not really mad about\Nwhat happened two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310247,1311164}Good!
Comment: 0,0:21:59.33,0:21:59.33,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1319339,1319339}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:04.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321800,1324052}{\i1}Do you remember, Lassie?
